印有『中華民國』字眼。」[1]<br />\n<br />\n前社長林偉棠先生指當時直播時，警察給予「溫馨提示」，以「擔心團體取出青天白日滿地紅旗會與其他人引起衝突」為由，阻止他們揮動中華民國國旗。團體中有人慾取出旗幟揮舞遭警察干預，支持者即時收回，但到最後宣佈結果時，支持者也不理會警察，取出大堆中華民國國旗舞動，警察也無可奈何。<br />\n<br />\n簡單啲講，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">青天白日滿地紅旗，同埋中華民國正統係匪共嘅春袋</span></strong>，大家十一想落中共面就要高舉高掛中華民國國旗同埋美國國旗！<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fyyo1Tr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ffyyo1Tr.jpg&h=20f5b021&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6xz31Tr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6xz31Tr.jpg&h=df523f2a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KgFKMj7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKgFKMj7.png&h=5214fd29&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5dd76c443735a6a6ff0c72d5d20799bf3eb3554f","tid":1586543,"uid":270506,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"0c704cbd92516ef8a734d8cf5a026cb857cb58df","tid":1586543,"uid":129445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T04:12:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NF1xZ7d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNF1xZ7d.jpg&h=b95e84d9&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T04:31:46.000Z","msg":"除左黑旗之外亦可考慮呢面旗：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8aP7O6K.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8aP7O6K.jpg&h=6513d2dc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我敢保證呢個場景重現香港會極震憾"},{"pid":"72321b48fa0a872729f37fdf5ff153a88d2e4a89","tid":1586543,"uid":238689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T04:32:27.000Z","msg":"無人講仲有一星期咋"},{"pid":"f68b85c4707bfd9dea65512dd4f14d29789c447f","tid":1586543,"uid":226103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T04:32:47.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"64b759a4228253152753f6ad8ec546a8cdd6c0bf","tid":1586543,"uid":38383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T04:33:19.000Z","msg":"痴撚線 今日活動都未完"},{"pid":"0a3582